summary: Just my game save with complete Daedric Armor, (Heavy) a house that I bought called Hjerim (Biggest house in skyrim) with all enhancements that could possibly purchase with the house. A Daedric greatsword (Legendary) with enchantments. Daedric bow with nearly 10000 Daedric arrows. Max level and level 100 in every skill (But Light Armor)
